{"tid":2094621,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"台灣其實沒有想像中的低薪","createTime":"2020-07-04T19:08:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-05T06:45:37.000Z","uid":351479,"like":13,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"bf2791095639b6474c45c423586e2795f4b801af","tid":2094621,"uid":351479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T19:08:08.000Z","msg":"打給後!哇細正港呆丸郎!<br />\n大家好!我是正港台灣人!<br />\n很多港仔一直說台灣低薪<br />\n我覺得真的是以偏概全<br />\n台灣低薪產業正好都是香港主要高薪產業(e.g.金融 /會計/行銷)<br />\n台灣的高薪產業(e.g.科技業/電子業...)，香港則是完全沒有，然後因為沒有所以也不認識<br />\n其實台灣如果做科技業，進台G(台積電)/發哥(聯發科)/豬屎屋(IC設計)...<br />\n起薪都是年薪25萬港幣起跳，做到經理150萬港幣，部經理300萬港幣...<br />\n所以不要一直覺得台灣低薪，是香港人大部份都不了解高薪的產業"},{"pid":"f250130f416ced6e53359249137e286999bbb102","tid":2094621,"uid":261796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T19:09:23.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"9e3082cfa844fee36d4c5569687ac6e43e4a35f9","tid":2094621,"uid":4519,"like":3,"dislike":16,"score":-13,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T19:21:27.000Z","msg":"25萬年薪，即係一個月得2萬，有幾高人工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"591ac2127c83ff511531ecf2b16af9e6ac3530c9","tid":2094621,"uid":58911,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"quote":{"pid":"9e3082cfa844fee36d4c5569687ac6e43e4a35f9","tid":2094621,"uid":4519,"like":3,"dislike":16,"score":-13,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T19:21:27.000Z","msg":"25萬年薪，即係一個月得2萬，有幾高人工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T19:23:41.000Z","msg":"8萬台紙係台北生活都算生活得幾好下喎"},{"pid":"ca27a1b911b6a03d68062dee0760489155381963","tid":2094621,"uid":6141,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"9e3082cfa844fee36d4c5569687ac6e43e4a35f9","tid":2094621,"uid":4519,"like":3,"dislike":16,"score":-13,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T19:21:27.000Z","msg":"25萬年薪，即係一個月得2萬，有幾高人工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.